title: unspecified error.
body: So I get an unspecific error when patching... Can anyone suggest a fix? Thanks

replies.body:
Hey there,

Can you provide your latest patcher log, located in the directory listed below. Feel free to put this on [pastebin](http://pastebin.com/) or send it as an email attachment to **oce-wrenchmen@googlegroups.com**, if emailing please include a link to your thread in the message.

>C:\Riot Games\League of Legends\Logs\Patcher Logs
